description.fr: Lorsqu'un adversaire subit une {#COLLISION}\_:\v{Summoning:171!} gagne autant d'{%AR} que de dégâts infligés. \--- Lorsqu'un {%Family_Taure_Name,plural:one} attaque\_: {#PUSH} la cible de {cell:c}. \--- {value:v,+,percent} aux DÉGÂTS de {#COLLISION} des {%Family_Taure_Name,plural:other}.
description.en: When an opponent endures a {#COLLISION}:\v{Summoning:171!} gains as much {%AR} as damage done. \--- When a {%Family_Taure_Name,plural:one} attacks: {#PUSH} the target {cell:c}. \--- {value:v,+,percent} to {%Family_Taure_Name,plural:other}' {#COLLISION} Damage.
